  "description": "## Deep Component Audit — hx-checkbox-group\n\n**Component directory:** `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-checkbox-group/`\n**NOTE:** This directory has NO index.ts — may be incomplete/from PR 175 rescue. Audit must verify if component exists and is functional.\n\n### Audit Scope\n1. **Existence Check** — Does this component have a complete implementation? If not, document what's missing.\n2. **Design Tokens** — `--hx-` tokens if implemented.\n3. **Accessibility** — WCAG 2.1 AA. role=\"group\". Group label. Error announcements.\n4. **Functionality** — Groups checkboxes. Min/max selection. Validation. Form integration.\n5. **TypeScript** — Strict. No `any`.\n6. **CSS/Styling** — Shadow DOM. Layout. Spacing between checkboxes.\n7. **CEM Accuracy** — Must be in CEM if shipping.\n8. **Tests** — Must exist.\n9. **Storybook** — Must exist.\n10. **Drupal Compatibility** — Twig-friendly.\n\n### Deliverable\nIf incomplete: document what exists, what's missing, and what needs to be built. If complete: full audit report.",
